Package: python3-linuxfd
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Python bindings for the Linux eventfd/signalfd/timerfd/inotify syscalls.
 This package provides python 3 bindings for syscalls suchs as eventfd,
 signalfd, timerfd and inotify. This can be used with selectors to build
 event driven python applications.
